## Déploiement Alternatif: Railway + Vercel

### Backend (Railway)

#### Configuration
Fichier : [railway.json](mdc:token4good-backend/railway.json)

#### Script Déploiement
```bash
cd token4good-backend
railway init
railway add -d postgres
./railway-deploy.sh
```

### Frontend (Vercel)

#### Configuration
Fichier : [vercel.json](mdc:vercel.json)

#### Script Déploiement
```bash
./deploy-vercel-v2.sh --prod
```

## Monitoring

### Health Checks
```bash
# Backend
curl https://api.token4good.com/health

# Frontend
curl https://app.token-for-good.com/api/health
```

### Logs
```bash
# Backend
railway logs --follow

# Frontend
vercel logs --follow
```

### Métriques à Surveiller
- API latency (p50, p95, p99)
- Error rate par endpoint
- Database connection pool
- Lightning payment success rate
- RGB contract creation rate

## Rollback Procedure
```bash
# Backend
railway rollback

# Frontend
vercel rollback
```

